  "description": "Fast, zero-config SAST CLI for Node.js backends. Detects SQLi, NoSQLi, XSS, RCE, path traversal, secrets, and 40+ other vulnerabilities via AST + taint analysis. Supports Express, NestJS, Fastify, Koa, Mongoose, TypeORM, Prisma.",
